{"tid":2425564,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美軍RC-135U戰略偵察機逼近廣東外海","createTime":"2021-02-27T12:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T16:43:41.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1c16f25debc07c246836271235f26fcd14f56c","tid":2425564,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:07:37.000Z","msg":"美軍RC-135U戰略偵察機逼近廣東外海<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國空軍一架RC-135U戰略偵察機飛近廣東外海偵察。<br />\n<br />\n內地智庫「南海戰略態勢感知」指，該偵察機早上由日本沖繩起飛，經巴士海峽飛到廣東外海偵察。最近距離中國劃定的領海基線不到47海里，刷新美國軍用飛機對中國抵近偵察距離最近的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n「南海戰略態勢感知」又指，對於美軍抵近偵察，中方要求美國要「適當顧及」。因為離中國太近，美軍執意抵近偵察，中國軍隊視距離遠近，通常也會採取跟蹤、伴飛和驅離等措施。<br />\n<br />\nRC-135U為電子情報偵察機，在機頭、翼端裝有天線，主要是執行搜集戰略電子偵察資訊任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=425564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425564&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=479f2450\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425564&h=6571cab3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=425564</a>"},{"pid":"5cc6bb40acf417d121df35ce8b84f8bba3f95b89","tid":2425564,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9r2ai8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9r2ai8.jpg&h=1f871d95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93d533ca724c4847d981577f09e7c749c965cc64","tid":2425564,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma